9
00:52:33.875 --> 00:52:50.935
Incoming livestream: So digital AI is more about acting on information, everything is on the screen, whereas physical AI, you are actually deploying it in the real world, and of course, when you go from a demo room to the real world, lots of things happen. Unprecedented things.

10
00:52:52.315 --> 00:52:58.145
