73
01:02:18.145 --> 01:02:30.855
Incoming livestream: I mean, think about, everybody is touting their tokens per second, right? Million tokens per second, or 4 million tokens per second. What is all that? It's, ultimately, it is how many tokens can you process per second that is the latency.

74
01:02:32.495 --> 01:02:39.935
Incoming livestream: In VLAs, You have your vision encoder models, you have the world models, and look at the timing there.

75
01:02:40.345 --> 01:02:49.485
Incoming livestream: The latency targets for these are sub-millisecond range. The entire loop, from sensing all the way to the control and the action.

76
01:02:49.965 --> 01:02:53.095
Incoming livestream: Is in… within 100 or 200 milliseconds.

77
01:02:54.575 --> 01:03:04.704
Incoming livestream: So this becomes very critical, that now VLAs are not evolving with, you know, the scalability of VLAs is not the size anymore. Rather, how fast can they go?

78
01:03:08.595 --> 01:03:15.985
Incoming livestream: And now, instead of saying that latency is a performance KPI, we talk about it as a safety parameter.

79
01:03:16.335 --> 01:03:20.684
Incoming livestream: Latency is a safety parameter, because you can be 100% right.

80
01:03:20.865 --> 01:03:28.595
Incoming livestream: But you can completely decide the right course of action, but if you come 10 milliseconds late, you're too late to the game.

81
01:03:28.935 --> 01:03:33.894
Incoming livestream: So, think about you're driving a car, and, you know, you know that you have to stop.

82
01:03:34.035 --> 01:03:40.385
Incoming livestream: At the stop sign, or a pedestrian suddenly, does a J… jaywalks around the thing.

83
01:03:41.045 --> 01:03:42.144
Incoming livestream: You have to stop.

84
01:03:43.275 --> 01:03:50.414
Incoming livestream: I mean, you can be perfectly right, you've sensed it, but if your reaction time is few minutes, few seconds, or milliseconds slow.

85
01:03:50.575 --> 01:03:52.974
Incoming livestream: Then you actually hit the pedestrian.

86
01:03:54.305 --> 01:04:08.495
Incoming livestream: In that entire pipeline, right, from the sensing till the control and action, there is a certain region where you can actually step back. Like, the world model has predicted, okay, this is the state it's going to be, LLM says this is a plan of action.

87
01:04:08.535 --> 01:04:20.035
