88
01:04:20.405 --> 01:04:21.855
Incoming livestream: You cannot reverse back.

89
01:04:23.095 --> 01:04:28.895
Incoming livestream: The… another aspect of this is why human in the air… human in the loop fails.

90
01:04:29.125 --> 01:04:36.085
