91
01:04:36.625 --> 01:04:43.144
Incoming livestream: Because humans cannot think in milliseconds. They are mostly in seconds and minutes.

92
01:04:43.915 --> 01:04:50.284
Incoming livestream: So basically, you need something in the architecture, in the entire software stack.

